 And, you know, another way to begin would be to just feel love and compassion

00:35:41.000 --> 00:35:45.000
 and develop that and thinking, you know, more about sentient beings

00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:49.000
 and like those who wish to be happy, all beings wish to be happy and contemplate.

