 this is Vajrayana, it's the total root, it's the complete foundation.

00:36:33.000 --> 00:36:37.000
 And if we can maintain that motivation and intention

00:36:37.000 --> 00:36:41.000
 and try to follow through with our practice that way, we won't,

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.000
 we'll never get off the path.

00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:48.000
 So I think it's just nice to just remember that refuge in the beginning

00:36:48.000 --> 00:36:53.000
 with that motivation of bodhicitta, and as Holiness, he even said that,

00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:58.000
 even a single mani, all mani from the home, you should dedicate that merit

00:36:58.000 --> 00:37:02.000
